Disneyland Railroad - Tomorrowland	
Donald's Boat	This boat is Donald's home. It's a lot of fun for kids to where our favorite sailor lives.
Dumbo the Flying Elephant	This spinner ride is popular for children. Each dumbo can be moved up and down by using a lever in front of the rider.
Walt Disney's Enchanted Tiki Room	The Tiki Room was the first public display of audio-animatronics. Food and drink are welcome in the show.
Fantasmic!	"Fantasmic! is a nighttime spectacular. Fireworks, laser lights, water screens, and live performance tell the story of Mickey's dream."
Fantasmic! Dining Packages	
Fantasy Faire	
Finding Nemo Submarine Voyage	This submarine provides a porthole view of the fantastic world under the ocean.
