Flag Retreat Ceremony	
Frontierland Shootin' Exposition	
Gadget's Go Coaster	This small roller coaster is a great introduction for kids to the world of thrill rides.
Goofy's Playhouse	"This home is just as goofy as its owner. It's a fun play ground, and a great place for kids to run around and get out their wiggles."
Get Your Ears On Celebration Dance Party	
Haunted Mansion	This chilling tour is filled with happy haunts. The ghosts are always willing to invite new friends to the mansion.
Haunted Mansion Holiday	The mansion is transformed by the collision of Halloween and Christmas. The cheerful chills are filled with both tricks and treats.
Horse-Drawn Streetcars, presented by National Car Rental	
Horseless Carriage, presented by National Car Rental	
Hyperspace Mountain	"When an X-wing squadron runs into a star destroyer, the pilots are thrown into a daring battle to defeat the Galactic Empire."
Indiana Jones Adventure	Indiana Jones combines motion simulator technology with a moving track. This ride has a fantastic mix of thrills and storytelling.
it's a small world	This ride was designed for the 1964 World's Fair. It is a message of world wide unity.
it's a small world Holiday	"This festive overlay to the classic ""it's a small world"" shows how holidays are celebrated around the world."
Jambalaya Jazz	
Jedi Training: Trials of the Temple	
Jingle Cruise	
Jungle Cruise	"A guided tour through the jungle. You'll encounter lions, elephants, zebras, and a few good jokes!"
King Arthur Carrousel	A classic carrousel in the heart of Fantasyland. Parents are welcome to stand next to their children.
Mad Tea Party	"A ""twist"" on the classic scrambled egg carnival ride. You get to control how quickly your tea cup spins."
Main Street Cinema	A small cinema showing Mickey Mouse cartoons. A calm place to sit down and relax.
Main Street Electrical Parade	
Main Street Piano Player	
Main Street Vehicles	
Mark Twain Riverboat	Take a trip around the Rivers of America on a steamboat. There are great views from all three levels.
Matterhorn Bobsleds	A jostling ride down Matterhorn mountain. The side closest to Fantasyland is a little bit gentler.
Meet Santa Claus at the Disneyland Resort	
Mickey and the Magical Map	"This live performance of song and dance takes Mickey on a journey to learn ""the secret of the map."""
Mickey's House and Meet Mickey	"Mickey's filming in the movie studio behind his house, but he invites everyone to walk through his home and yard to meet him there."
